{{zh-forms|[[送]][[君]][[千]][[里]]，[[终]][[须]][[一]][[别]]|[[送君千里，終須一別]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: Even if you see a friend off for a thousand [[w:li (unit)|li]], in the end you still have to part.
===Proverb===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' sòng jūn qiān lĭ, zhōng xū yì bié)
# It is time for us to part company.
